USEPATTERN:
   * login (possible register with email/nick)
   * invite friend
   * initiate duel-request to server
   * both users are 'ready'
   * server synchronizes both clients
   * server notifies clients of countdown
   * clients send back time of action
   * server determines winner
   * server keeps stats

FUTURE
   * QR Code
   * graphics
   * push notification
   * cheat detection


